description: EncounterCare Solutions, Inc. operates as an energy and healthcare company in the United States. It operates through Energy and Healthcare Services divisions. The Energy division produces and distributes a fuel additive under the EcoFlex 96 and Dynamo brand names. The Healthcare Services division offers a suite of pediatric and neonatal services, including skilled nursing, home infusion, medical equipment, and others. The company was formerly known as Ecare Solutions, Inc. and changed its name to EncounterCare Solutions, Inc. in November 2000. EncounterCare Solutions, Inc. is headquartered in Palm Beach Gardens, Florida.
